snippet.title: Cecè Barretta - Gioia Mia Ranna
snippet.description:
Immergiti in questa pura magia di “Gioia Mia Ranna”
Questa canzone parla di qualcosa che sembra un sogno, ma forse è reale.  
Di una presenza che si sente, che non fa rumore ma lascia la scia di emozioni.  
È come una magia, non sai se la stai vivendo davvero o se la stai solo immaginando o sognando.  
Ma ti prende l’anima, ti guida dolcemente, ti resta dentro.  
(È quella sensazione che ti fa sorridere senza motivo, che ti manca anche se non è mai stata davvero tua.)  
Una sensazione che riaffiora nei momenti più inattesi, quando meno te lo aspetti, quasi come un ricordo che non hai scelto ma che torna da solo, come un sussurro nella mente. Qualcosa che non sai spiegare, come se ti sfiorasse il cuore e resta lì, silenziosamente. 
Come un soffio delicato che ti tocca l’anima, una luce che si accende nel buio e ti lascia con il cuore sospeso, tra il desiderio di credere e la paura di sognare troppo!
E forse, anche tu, stai ancora cercando di capire se era amore… o solo un incantesimo.🧚‍♀️



testo:
sei come un ombra che mi guida dolcemente
non so se ancora questo esiste veramente

quel desiderio che mi strazia e mi tormenta
fa male tanto ma è bello e cosi intenso

nasci col sole e poi sparisci al tramonto
vena ra notti e d'intra u liattu u pijju suannu
e mi lizu stancu a furia di pinzari a tia 
ma chi follia

gioia mia ranna  gioia ranna mia
sulu tu mi fa scurdari tutti cazzi mia
gioia mia bella  gioia bella mia
sulu tu mi fa arraggiari u sangua miiiiia 

perché tu sei come il sale dentro il mare
picchi tu si cumu na terra da scoprire
perché tu sei la cosa che non può mancare
picchi tu si si troppu bella da morire

tu si la fiamma ca m'illumina intra u scuru
tu ca mi fa scurdari ogni e pena e duluri
tu si l'ispirazioni tu si la poesia
tu si magia

gioia mia ranna  gioia ranna mia
sulu tu mi fa scurdari tutti cazzi mia
gioia mia bella gioia bella mia
sulu tu mi fa arraggiari u sangua miiiiia

questa passione che mi avvolge è sorprendente
la voglio vivere silenziosamente 
sei dentro l'anima anche se non sei vicino
e seguo il cuore sulla strada del mio destino

e tu si chira ca quannu mi lizu si u primu pinsiari
e tu si chira ca quannu mi guardi mi fa incantare
e tu si chira ca quannu ti ciarcu mi fai danzare 
mi fai sognare mi fai volare e mi fai volare

gioia mia ranna  gioia ranna mia
sulu tu mi fa scurdari tutti cazzi mia
gioia mia bella  gioia bella mia
sulu tu mi fa arraggiari u sangua miiiiia

snippet.title: Ti uccideranno | Trailer Ufficiale
snippet.description:
Chi sarà il prossimo a essere sacrificato? #TiUcciderannoIlFilm solo al cinema dal 26 marzo.

Da New Line Cinema e Nocturna arriva TI UCCIDERANNO. Il film porta sul grande schermo un horror-action-comedy ad alto tasso di adrenalina e intriso di sangue, in cui una giovane donna deve sopravvivere alla notte al Virgil - il covo misterioso e oscuro di un culto demoniaco - prima di essere sacrificata. Ne nasce uno scontro cinematografico audace e senza freni, tra uccisioni efferate e un umorismo nerissimo.

Nel cast di TI UCCIDERANNO troviamo Zazie Beetz, Myha’La, Paterson Joseph, Tom Felton, Heather Graham e Patricia Arquette.

Diretto da Kirill Sokolov e scritto da Sokolov e Alex Litvak, il film è prodotto da Andy Muschietti, Barbara Muschietti e Dan Kagan. I produttori esecutivi sono Russell Ackerman, John Schoenfelder, Carl Hampe, Litvak e Sokolov.

Dietro la macchina da presa, Sokolov è affiancato dal direttore della fotografia Isaac Bauman, dallo scenografo Jeremy Reed, dall'editor Luke Doolan, dal costumista Neil McClean e dal supervisore degli effetti visivi Marc Smith. Le musiche sono di Carlos Rafael Rivera, la supervisione musicale è di Andrea von Foerster e il casting è a cura di Richard Delia.

New Line Cinema e Nocturna presentano TI UCCIDERANNO, distribuito da Warner Bros. Pictures, solo al cinema dal 26 marzo 2026.

snippet.title: George Michael - Careless Whisper (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
#carelesswhisper #georgemichael #lyrics #S&R #tiktok #viral 
George Michael - Careless Whisper (Lyrics)

[Intro]
Time can never mend
The careless whispers
Of a good friend
To the heart and mind
Ignorance is kind
There's no comfort in the truth
Pain is all you'll find
Should've known better, yeah

[Instrumental]

[Verse 1]
I feel so unsure
As I take your hand
And lead you to the dance floor
As the music dies
Something in your eyes
Calls to mind a silver screen
And all its sad goodbyes

[Chorus]
I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
Should've known better than to cheat a friend
And waste a chance that I've been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Verse 2]
Time can never mend
The careless whispers
Of a good friend
To the heart and mind
Ignorance is kind
There's no comfort in the truth
Pain is all you'll find

[Chorus]
I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
Should've known better than to cheat a friend
(Should've known better, yeah)
And waste a chance that I've been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Post-Chorus]
Never without your love

[Bridge]
Tonight, the music seems so loud
I wish that we could lose this crowd
Maybe it's better this way
We'd hurt each other with the things we want to say
We could have been so good together
We could have lived this dance forever
But now, who's gonna dance with me?
Please stay

[Chorus]
And I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
Should've known better than to cheat a friend
And waste a chance that I've been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Outro]
(Now that you're gone)
Now that you're gone
(Now that you're gone)
Was what I did so wrong, so wrong
That you had to leave me alone?

— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— Avengers: Doomsday - X-Men Trailer

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers Doomsday X-Men, the story unfolds in a world that believes the age of heroes has already passed, only to discover that a far greater reckoning has begun. Following years of uneasy silence, the destruction of the X-Men’s legacy forces an older, battle-worn Professor Charles Xavier to confront the failure of his dream, leading him to reunite with an equally hardened Magneto as a new global threat targets mutantkind with ruthless precision. As humanity’s fear evolves into policy and survival becomes a matter of extinction, the conflict expands beyond old rivalries, drawing the remnants of the Avengers into a war defined by inevitability rather than hope. The emergence of unstoppable sentinels signals a future where evolution itself is under siege, and the emotional breaking point arrives when Cyclops loses control of his power on the battlefield, symbolizing the cost of repression and the beginning of open war. Together, the trailer frames a turning point where ideals collapse, alliances are reforged, and the fight is no longer for peace, but for the right to exist.

snippet.title: [Official Trailer] เปย์รักด้วยแมวเลี้ยง Cat For Cash
snippet.description:
ไทเกอร์ (เฟิร์ส คณพันธ์) เจ้าหนี้หนุ่มทาสแมวหัวใจคุณธรรม ได้รับสืบทอดพลังพิเศษ ‘สามารถสื่อสารกับแมวได้’ จาก เจ๊เหมียว (เฟรช อริศรา) เจ้าของร้านคาเฟ่แมว ก่อนที่เจ๊เหมียวจะเสียชีวิตเหล่าแมวๆ ขอร้องให้ไทเกอร์รักษาร้านไว้จาก ลิงซ์ (ข้าวตัง ธนวัฒน์) ลูกชายของเจ๊เหมียวที่กำลังจะเซ้งร้าน และมีตัวแปรสำคัญอย่าง เลโอ (สตางค์ กิตติภพ) น้องชายต่างแม่ของลิงซ์ กับหมอปอม (เกรท สพล) สัตวแพทย์สุดหล่อ เข้ามาทำให้เกิดเรื่องราวมากมาย ทั้งเรื่องการร่วมมือกันทำคาเฟ่แมวและความเข้าใจกันในครอบครัว

 ภาษาแมวจะทำให้ความรักก่อตัวอย่างไร ติดตามได้ในซีรีส์ ‘เปย์รักด้วยแมวเลี้ยง’
ทุกวันอังคาร เวลา 20:30 น. ทางช่อง GMM25 และทางแอปพลิเคชั่น TrueVisions NOW เท่านั้น เริ่มตอนแรก 20 มกราคมนี้

กำกับซีรีส์ : กรพรหม นิยมศิลป์

รายชื่อนักแสดง

เจเจ ชยกร จุฑามาศ    รับบท  กระป๊อ

ไทเกอร์ (เฟิร์ส คณพันธ์) เจ้าหนี้หนุ่มทาสแมวหัวใจคุณธรรม ได้รับสืบทอดพลังพิเศษ ‘สามารถสื่อสารกับแมวได้’ จาก เจ๊เหมียว (เฟรช อริศรา) เจ้าของร้านคาเฟ่แมว ก่อนที่เจ๊เหมียวจะเสียชีวิตเหล่าแมวๆ ขอร้องให้ไทเกอร์รักษาร้านไว้จาก ลิงซ์ (ข้าวตัง ธนวัฒน์) ลูกชายของเจ๊เหมียวที่กำลังจะเซ้งร้าน และมีตัวแปรสำคัญอย่าง เลโอ (สตางค์ กิตติภพ) น้องชายต่างแม่ของลิงซ์ กับหมอปอม (เกรท สพล) สัตวแพทย์สุดหล่อ เข้ามาทำให้เกิดเรื่องราวมากมาย ทั้งเรื่องการร่วมมือกันทำคาเฟ่แมวและความเข้าใจกันในครอบครัว

 ภาษาแมวจะทำให้ความรักก่อตัวอย่างไร ติดตามได้ในซีรีส์ ‘เปย์รักด้วยแมวเลี้ยง’
ทุกวันอังคาร เวลา 20:30 น. ทางช่อง GMM25 และทางแอปพลิเคชั่น TrueVisions NOW เท่านั้น เริ่มตอนแรก 20 มกราคมนี้

กำกับซีรีส์ : กรพรหม นิยมศิลป์

รายชื่อนักแสดง
เฟิร์ส คณพันธ์ ปุ้ยตระกูล   รับบท  ไทเกอร์
ข้าวตัง ธนวัฒน์ รัตนกิจไพศาล   รับบท  ลิงซ์ 
สตางค์ กิตติภพ เสรีวิชยสวัสดิ์   รับบท  เลโอ
เฟรช อริศรา วงษ์ชาลี    รับบท  เจ๊เหมียว
เจเจ ชยกร จุฑามาศ    รับบท  กระป๊อ   
เกรท สพล อัศวมั่นคง  รับบท  หมอปอม
